flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Completion of production line activities requiring quality inspection.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect operator inspection results]
  N1 --> N2[Agent: Agentic AI - Analyze automated vision system data]
  N2 --> N3[Agent: Agentic AI - Perform end-of-line diagnostics]
  N3 --> N4[Agent: Agentic AI - Evaluate attribute gaging results]
  N4 --> N5{Agent: Agentic AI - Make quality certification decision}
  N5 -->|Primary| N6[PB: Remote Functions - Route products for rework or release]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced scrap, rework, and downtime, improved OTIF and COGS efficiency。]
  N5 -->|Operator inspection fails| B1[Route item for rework]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Item is flagged for rework and sent back to the production line]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Automated vision system detects defect| B2[Flag item for further inspection]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Item is flagged for additional inspection and potential rework]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Diagnostic test identifies fault| B3[Route item for repair]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Item is routed for repair and retesting before release]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]